included.description:
Vocal Minority is a giving circle, dedicated to funding equity and justice and America. Each month, all members share, discuss, and eventually select an organization to contribute to. By pooling our resources in this way, we are capable of making a substantial impact for an organization. 

Here's how it works:

- Selection: Once a month, an issue area and nonprofit are discussed and selected
- Donations: Members contribute their donations into the Vocal Minority Fund
- Grant: A grant is made at the end of the month to our selected nonprofit

To date, we've donated more than $65K to organizations all over the United States.
included.title: Vocal Minority
